OL,3,C'Astonishing' final total raised for
OL,4,Cgirl orphaned by crash revealed
OL,6,FA fundraiser launched to support an 11-
OL,7,Fyear-old girl who was orphaned after a
OL,8,Fcrash has closed after reaching more
OL,9,Fthan #408,000.
OL,11,FPoppie Roller was at her best friend's
OL,12,Fhome when her parents and two sisters
OL,13,Fwere involved in a collision with a
OL,14,Fmotorbike on the A61 between Wakefield
OL,15,Fand Barnsley on 21 July.
OL,17,FAll four died at the scene, along with
OL,18,Fthe couple who were riding the bike.
