OL,3,C'Astonishing' final total raised for
OL,4,Cgirl orphaned by crash revealed
OL,6,FAfter the incident, Paul Hepple - the
OL,7,Fstep father of Poppie's best friend -
OL,8,Fset up an online fundraiser with the
OL,9,Faim of collecting #3,000 to support
OL,10,Fher with living expenses, counselling
OL,11,Fand education.
OL,13,FThe Go Fund Me page quickly surpassed
OL,14,Fthat figure and eventually closed on
OL,15,FFriday, 11 October, having raised an
OL,16,F"astonishing" #408,207.
OL,18,FWriting on the page, Mr Hepple praised
OL,19,Fdonors "incredible generosity".
