OL,3,C'Astonishing' final total raised for
OL,4,Cgirl orphaned by crash revealed
OL,6,FHe said: "I never could have imagined
OL,7,Fthe outpouring of love and support
OL,8,Fthat followed.
OL,10,F"There have been 22,500 donations from
OL,11,Fpeople all over the world... It's
OL,12,Ftruly remarkable."
OL,14,FHe said "every single penny" would be
OL,15,Fput into a trust fund, managed by
OL,16,FPoppie's aunt Faye, who is now caring
OL,17,Ffor her.
OL,19,FMr Hepple said Poppie was doing "as
OL,20,Fwell as can be expected under the
OL,21,Fcircumstances".
