OL,3,C'Astonishing' final total raised for
OL,4,Cgirl orphaned by crash revealed
OL,6,F"She has bravely returned to school
OL,7,Fand, although she was nervous at
OL,8,Ffirst, she is slowly settling in," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe road safety charity Brake has been
OL,12,Fsupporting Poppie.
OL,14,FIn a message to supporters, Mr Hepple
OL,15,Fadded: Thank you all from the bottom
OL,16,Fof my heart for your continued
OL,17,Fkindness, patience, and support. Your
OL,18,Fgenerosity has not only secured
OL,19,FPoppie's future but has also brought
OL,20,Flight during a very dark time.
